Alphabet Triangle

public class AlphabetTriangle {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {

            char ch = 'A';

            for (int j = 1; j <= i; j++) {
                System.out.print(ch + " ");
                ch++;
            }

            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}

Output
A
A B
A B C
A B C D
A B C D E
